The '''Tursha''' were a [[Humanoid/Legends|humanoid]] species distinguished by their [[Lekku/Legends|head-tails]] and eleven-fingered hands. One of them was a [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] who tried to capture [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] and [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] on their training exercise on [[Ragoon VI|Ragoon-6]] using a [[Spray stick/Legends|stokhli stick]] to paralyze them. He was killed in [[27 BBY/Legends|27 BBY]] with a fast poison injected in the neck.

